Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,ん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.95,0:11:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,あ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,うあ　あ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.70,0:11:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,お母さん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.08,0:11:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,ごめんね　私は君のお母さんじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.75,0:11:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,幻覚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,幻覚じゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,んん…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.16,0:11:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,はっ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,う
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,うぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.83,0:11:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,あ　そうだ 謝らなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.79,0:11:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-かっ　ああああああ\N-あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.95,0:11:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,なんでいつも逃げちゃうの？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,むっ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.70,0:11:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,戻ったか アイズ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:11:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,どうだ ちゃんと謝れたか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.25,0:12:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,…ちゃった
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.37,0:12:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,何？
