Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,ぷっ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-ふっ ふふふふ\N-ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-ふっ ふふふふふ\N-むう
